NEW YORK, NY ? Grammy award-winning singer-songwriter Sheryl Crow graces the June issue of Country Living?along with her rescue dog, Benji?and opens the doors to her 50-acre Nashville property?which includes a house, a church, and a barn?to take readers on a tour filled with unexpected finds from a lifetime of junking.
